SUMMARY:🟡 Form 1023-EZ — Target Filing Date
DESCRIPTION:501(c)(3) application.\n$275 fee.\nDeadline: ~Jul 3 2028 (27-month window) but target Sep 2026.\nPrereqs: Board expanded, all policies adopted, bylaws updated.\nEligibility: gross receipts ≤$50K, assets ≤$250K.\nFile at pay.gov
LOCATION:https://www.pay.gov/public/form/start/29067782
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CATEGORIES:HIGH,IRS
